{"tid":1942950,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"二十國集團領導人明將以視像會議舉行武肺特別峰會 習近平出席","createTime":"2020-03-25T11:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T12:06:13.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c3c0623932404cbf83033b66a7a0509da743df","tid":1942950,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】二十國集團領導人周四以視像會議方式，舉行應對新型肺炎特別峰會，國家主席習近平會參與。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國秘書長古特雷斯在會前去信二十國集團領袖，呼籲各國增加資源，協助受疫情打擊的貧窮國家。<br />\n<br />\n外電引述古特雷斯信件，促請二十國領袖採取措施，包括推出數以萬億美元計的刺激經濟方案，禁止實施關稅、配額以及其他貿易限制，撤銷對部分國家實施的制裁，確保食物及醫療物資等必需品可以流通，協助發展中的貧窮國家。<br />\n<br />\n古特雷斯指二十國集團國家是全球主要的經濟體，應該在對抗疫情大流行中肩負重要角色，如果二十國領袖不伸出援手，全球都會受影響，二十國都不可能幸免。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=385574\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385574&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Bynx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=426123df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385574&h=1f357363\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=385574</a>"},{"pid":"7ad681b39b4826975a38b16b224c3a895c3df509","tid":1942950,"uid":187957,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:03:23.000Z","msg":"習近平出席做乜？"},{"pid":"403a4692cf5c568c8860683ad712f75f3b6fd4b8","tid":1942950,"uid":187957,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:03:56.000Z","msg":"概念圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b3ampCB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb3ampCB.jpg&h=d0e7fa2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b1cb4cf9d1d900414c88bb3467af40fd83e1057","tid":1942950,"uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7ad681b39b4826975a38b16b224c3a895c3df509","tid":1942950,"uid":187957,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:03:23.000Z","msg":"習近平出席做乜？"},"citedBy":1